Reasonable but quite touristy and commercial
Quite touristy and commercial. Make sure you head to the back of the main hotels in BaiChay to see where the locals eat, and get more authentic food. Worth a visit, but probably not somewhere to spend a whole heap of time.
Review of: Bai Chay Commercial Center
Written December 28, 2018
